## üì∏ Upload Images (‡∏£‡∏π‡∏õ‡∏†‡∏≤‡∏û)

### 1. Upload ‡∏£‡∏π‡∏õ‡∏†‡∏≤‡∏û‡∏Ñ‡∏£‡∏∏‡∏†‡∏±‡∏ì‡∏ë‡πå (‡∏ï‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏á Login)
```
POST /upload/asset/{asset_id}
Headers: Authorization: Bearer {token}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data
```
**Form Data:**
```
image: [FILE]
```
**Response:**
```json
{
    "success": true,
    "message": "‡∏≠‡∏±‡∏õ‡πÇ‡∏´‡∏•‡∏î‡∏£‡∏π‡∏õ‡∏†‡∏≤‡∏û‡∏™‡∏≥‡πÄ‡∏£‡πá‡∏à",
    "data": {
        "filename": "asset_abc123.jpg",
        "filepath": "uploads/assets/asset_abc123.jpg",
        "url": "http://localhost/.../uploads/assets/asset_abc123.jpg"
    }
}
```

### 2. Upload ‡∏´‡∏•‡∏≤‡∏¢‡∏£‡∏π‡∏õ‡∏û‡∏£‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏°‡∏Å‡∏±‡∏ô (‡∏ï‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏á Login)
```
POST /upload/multiple
Headers: Authorization: Bearer {token}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data
```
**Form Data:**
```
images[]: [FILE1]
images[]: [FILE2]
images[]: [FILE3]
```
**Response:**
```json
{
    "success": true,
    "message": "‡∏≠‡∏±‡∏õ‡πÇ‡∏´‡∏•‡∏î‡πÄ‡∏™‡∏£‡πá‡∏à‡∏™‡∏¥‡πâ‡∏ô",
    "data": {
        "uploaded": [
            {"filename": "asset_1.jpg", "url": "http://..."},
            {"filename": "asset_2.jpg", "url": "http://..."}
        ],
        "errors": [],
        "total": 2,
        "failed": 0
    }
}
```

### 3. ‡∏•‡∏ö‡∏£‡∏π‡∏õ‡∏†‡∏≤‡∏û‡∏Ñ‡∏£‡∏∏‡∏†‡∏±‡∏ì‡∏ë‡πå (‡∏ï‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏á Login)
```
DELETE /upload/asset/{asset_id}
Headers: Authorization: Bearer {token}
```
**Response:**
```json
{
    "success": true,
    "message": "‡∏•‡∏ö‡∏£‡∏π‡∏õ‡∏†‡∏≤‡∏û‡∏™‡∏≥‡πÄ‡∏£‡πá‡∏à"
}
```

### ‡∏Ç‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏Å‡∏≥‡∏´‡∏ô‡∏î‡∏£‡∏π‡∏õ‡∏†‡∏≤‡∏û
- **‡∏õ‡∏£‡∏∞‡πÄ‡∏†‡∏ó‡πÑ‡∏ü‡∏•‡πå**: JPG, JPEG, PNG, GIF
- **‡∏Ç‡∏ô‡∏≤‡∏î‡πÑ‡∏°‡πà‡πÄ‡∏Å‡∏¥‡∏ô**: 5MB
- **‡∏Ç‡∏ô‡∏≤‡∏î‡∏™‡∏π‡∏á‡∏™‡∏∏‡∏î**: 1920x1080 px (‡∏à‡∏∞‡∏ñ‡∏π‡∏Å resize ‡∏≠‡∏±‡∏ï‡πÇ‡∏ô‡∏°‡∏±‡∏ï‡∏¥)
- **‡∏à‡∏±‡∏î‡πÄ‡∏Å‡πá‡∏ö‡∏ó‡∏µ‡πà**: `uploads/assets/`

---

## üß™ ‡∏ï‡∏±‡∏ß‡∏≠‡∏¢‡πà‡∏≤‡∏á‡∏Å‡∏≤‡∏£ Upload ‡∏î‡πâ‡∏ß‡∏¢ JavaScript

### Upload ‡∏£‡∏π‡∏õ‡∏†‡∏≤‡∏û‡πÄ‡∏î‡∏µ‡∏¢‡∏ß
```javascript
const uploadImage = async (assetId, file) => {
    const formData = new FormData();
    formData.append('image', file);

    const response = await fetch(`${API_BASE}/upload/asset/${assetId}`, {
        method: 'POST',
        headers: {
            'Authorization': `Bearer ${token}`
        },
        body: formData
    });
    
    return await response.json();
};

// ‡πÉ‡∏ä‡πâ‡∏á‡∏≤‡∏ô
const fileInput = document.querySelector('input[type="file"]');
const file = fileInput.files[0];
const result = await uploadImage(1, file);
console.log(result);
```

### Upload ‡∏´‡∏•‡∏≤‡∏¢‡∏£‡∏π‡∏õ
```javascript
const uploadMultiple = async (files) => {
    const formData = new FormData();
    
    for (let file of files) {
        formData.append('images[]', file);
    }

    const response = await fetch(`${API_BASE}/upload/multiple`, {
        method: 'POST',
        headers: {
            'Authorization': `Bearer ${token}`
        },
        body: formData
    });
    
    return await response.json();
};
```

